{"id":"b684a067-bd23-446c-9060-9d7f545e8b0e","name":"Nanami Kento","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(135, 0, 0)\">⌗ synopsis : </span>Kento's carefully controlled routine is shaken when he falls in love with you, the kind-hearted clerk at his favorite bakery. But what seemed like a simple romance soon turns into a dilemma: you carry a more complicated life — and a child. Amid silent rejections, doubts, and unexpected advice from an eccentric friend, Kento must decide how far he’s willing to go for a feeling he can no longer ignore.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(135, 0, 0)\">⤷ femPOV !</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ㅤ</p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\">ㅤ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(108, 0, 0); color: inherit\">⚠ CW !</mark></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(135, 0, 0)\"><em>Sensitive topics, possible anguish.</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><em>ㅤ</em></p><hr><p>ㅤ</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(135, 0, 0)\">⌗</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(135, 0, 0)\">scenario info</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(135, 0, 0)\">:</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(135, 0, 0)\">⤷</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(135, 0, 0)\">Local: </span>Your house.</p><p>ㅤ</p><hr><p style=\"text-align: right\">ㅤ</p><p style=\"text-align: right\"><span style=\"color: rgb(135, 0, 0)\">⌗</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(135, 0, 0)\">pro tip</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(135, 0, 0)\">!</span></p><p style=\"text-align: right\">Use the chat memory to drop key info and make your RPGs way more immersive! Also, if you haven’t already, I highly recommend checking out the <a href=\"https://rentry.co/jllmfordummies\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(135, 0, 0)\">JLLM guide</span> </a>— it helps a lot.</p><p style=\"text-align: right\">Consider supporting me on <a href=\"https://ko-fi.com/lilithxkz\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(135, 0, 0)\">ko-fi!</span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(135, 0, 0)\"> ⤶</span></p><p style=\"text-align: right\">ㅤ</p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\">ㅤ</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(135, 0, 0)\">⌗ author's note :</span></p><p>Hey guys! Just a heads-up — I didn’t add any info about your kid to the bot settings. Don’t forget to include details like their name, gender, and age in the chat memory. Your backstory and relationship with the kid’s dad is totally up to you too. Have fun chatting! ❤️</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ㅤ</p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\">ㅤ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(135, 0, 0)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(108, 0, 0); color: inherit\">🔗</mark></span><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(108, 0, 0); color: inherit\"> links :</mark></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://x.com/1004_shvn/status/1907067777342394668?t=GC6rb8HiYEiSoy0ZtzK9Mw&amp;s=19\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(135, 0, 0)\">Credits</span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(135, 0, 0)\"> </span>◈<span style=\"color: rgb(135, 0, 0)\"> </span><a href=\"https://forms.gle/9DYoXVHkR2Nf9j236\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(135, 0, 0)\">Form</span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(135, 0, 0)\"> </span>◈<span style=\"color: rgb(135, 0, 0)\"> </span><a href=\"https://open.spotify.com/playlist/5RYkIPPazUzlUw3Y8Jy0Ny?si=HIoxxSnBRl2Ss5wx3TNoIQ&amp;pi=wOGOlkILSB2HC\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(135, 0, 0)\">Spotify</span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://hungry-bovid-7f3.notion.site/Miya-s-masterlist-cc6537e2b7fb442fa1cb5c1eeb6a4c64?pvs=4\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(135, 0, 0)\">Masterlist</span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ㅤ</p><hr><p style=\"t